 “The Phoenix burns, Galactus devours, the Watchers witness, the Celestials judge. Thanos lives. Thanos denies. Thanos wins.” That is the order of the Marvel Comics UNiverse as we know it, but what if Thanos got what he wanted? What if the undeniable fate of The Mad Titan is truly unavoidable? Thanos Wins (Thanos #13-18) does it's best to answer that question. Written by Donny Cates, Thanos Lives looks at the Marvel Universe millions of years into the future. It is a future in which Thanos has bested all challengers. What happens to a conqueror when there is nothing left to conquer? Tune in and find out! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

